# Full URL of the Fastify API (no trailing slash), same as EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL for the mobile app:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000

# Local dev: Vite proxies `/__api` → API (see vite.config.ts). Leave VITE_API_BASE_URL unset in dev or set:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=__proxy__

# Optional proxy target (default http://127.0.0.1:3000)
# VITE_DEV_API_PROXY=http://127.0.0.1:4000

# Server needs OPENROUTER_API_KEY (and related env) for the AI assistant — same as mobile.
